      <div class="badCellDesc">
      <h1>Abnormal Blood Cells</h1>


      <p>
      The misshaped red blood cell
      causes obstructions in blood
      vessels. The sickle-shaped
      cells cluster together which can
      block blood flow.
      </p>
      <br>
      <h1>Normal Blood Cells</h1>
      <p>
      Healthy red blood
      cells carry oxygen
      throughout the body.
      </p>
      </div>

